reviewText: Being from Brooklyn I love anything to do with it.  I sent this as a gift to a family member who I know loved receiving it.  Thanks for the prompt delivery.
If you are a Yankees or Dodgers fan, you will like this

The documentary is a bit sparse.  And, I was a bit disappointed by the fact that there was no footage from the 2000 World series.

But, there was some classic footage on there that made it worthwhile.
This video takes me back to my childhood!
